# 🧘‍♀️ Yoga Studio

Welcome to **Yoga Studio** — a beautifully designed, responsive single-page website for a modern Yoga Studio, Instructor, or Wellness Center.

This project combines clean **frontend development** with a **Django backend** for easy deployment and future scalability.

---

## 🌟 **Features**

✅ Single-page premium design  
✅ Hero banner with call-to-action  
✅ Yoga styles/cards grid section  
✅ Instructor bio section  
✅ Video background section  
✅ Customer reviews/testimonials  
✅ Contact form at the bottom:
   - Name
   - Phone Number
   - Email
   - Book Seat / Join Now button
   - Attractive shadow, hover effect & modern typography

✅ Fully **mobile responsive** layout with Flipkart/Amazon style grid breakpoints  
✅ Easy to customize & scale for real client projects

---

## 📊 **Tech Stack**

| **Languages & Tools** | **Percentage** |
|------------------------|-----------------|
| **CSS**               | 46.9%           |
| **JavaScript**        | 42.4%           |
| **HTML**              | 6.6%            |
| **Python (Django)**   | 4.1%            |

> 📝 **Note:** This project is intentionally frontend-heavy to showcase strong design and responsiveness.
Django backend is used for serving templates and managing static files — ready to scale with more backend logic in future.

